    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Agentic Content Team \u2014 VKZ Automations\n\n**Trigger:** Send a Telegram message with your content topic.\nExample: `AI automation for restaurants`\n\n**What happens:**\n1. \ud83d\udd0d Research Agent \u2014 finds key facts and the best angle\n2. \u270d\ufe0f Writer Agent \u2014 writes the LinkedIn post (150-250 words)\n3. \ud83c\udfaf Critic Agent \u2014 scores it 0-10. If < 7, rewrites automatically (max 2 times)\n4. \ud83d\udccb Sends draft to Telegram \u2014 you read it, then tap Approve or Reject\n5. \u2705 Approve \u2192 saves to Google Docs + logs to Sheets + posts to LinkedIn\n   \u274c Reject \u2192 rewrites with your rejection noted, sends a new draft",
        "height": 380,
        "width": 620
      },
